{"type":"text","timestamp":1779168082911,"sessionID":"ses_1c15753b5ffe0uF0tU9Lf0PCIg","part":{"id":"prt_e3eae54c6001WVPaMWg4eLPNyb","messageID":"msg_e3eae495c001xD82HTguLkd5U2","sessionID":"ses_1c15753b5ffe0uF0tU9Lf0PCIg","type":"text","text":"File created and verified at `.claude-project/nestfind/docs/PROJECT_DATABASE.md`.\n\n**Schema covers 9 entities** derived from the API shapes and feature set:\n\n| Entity | Table | Purpose |\n|--------|-------|---------|\n| User | `users` | Renter + Admin accounts (UUID PK, soft delete, role/status enums) |\n| RefreshToken | `refresh_tokens` | JWT rotation with `revoked_at` for invalidation |\n| PasswordResetToken | `password_reset_tokens` | Forgot-password flow with `expires_at` + `used_at` |\n| Property | `properties` | Rental listings with denormalized address columns and geo-coords |\n| PropertyPhoto | `property_photos` | Photo gallery with `is_primary` and `sort_order` |\n| Amenity | `amenities` | Predefined amenity catalog (name + icon) |\n| PropertyAmenity | `property_amenities` | M:N junction linking properties to amenities |\n| Favorite | `favorites` | Renter bookmarks with composite unique on `(user_id, property_id)` |\n| Inquiry | `inquiries` | Contact submissions with denormalized submitter fields and admin response tracking |\n\nIncludes all 4 enums (`RoleEnum`, `UserStatusEnum`, `PropertyTypeEnum`, `InquiryStatusEnum`), indexes for every queried column, FK summary table, and relationship diagram.","time":{"start":1779168072902,"end":1779168082909}}}
